title: Cairn Bannoch
text: Cairn Bannoch is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in the <a href="Grampian%20Mountains%20%28Scotland%29">Grampians</a> of <a href="Scotland">Scotland</a>, located about seventeen miles south of the <a href="River%20Dee%2C%20Aberdeenshire">River Dee</a> near <a href="Balmoral%20Castle">Balmoral</a>.
